narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Probably required but a good class overall
You have to take it if you're chemE abet.

Compared to the other ChemE classes that you've probably taken, this isn't too bad in terms of materials and workload. The second half of the class consists mostly of working on your senior design project, which isn't too time-consuming. You are assigned a group to work with for your senior project. A lot of the project requires self-learning because there is not too much direction from the Professors, but it was also a good experience to work with your group for the project.
